      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>RICHHEIMER--Ivy. The Merrick Jewish Centre mourns the passing of our dear member Ivy Richheimer, and extends heartfelt condolences to her beloved husband Alan, children Todd, Evan, Brett, sister Wendy Jacobs, and brother Lloyd Hersch. We pray they will be consoled with all the mourners of our people. Linda Altman, President Rabbi Charles A. Klein</p>
